Old prayers.

73
00:06:16.476 --> 00:06:17.712
Before God prayers?

74
00:06:19.247 --> 00:06:21.816
No. There was always God.

75
00:06:22.382 --> 00:06:24.252
Just country prayers.

76
00:06:24.585 --> 00:06:25.920
- Berrow prayers.
- Grace: (chuckles)

77
00:06:26.320 --> 00:06:28.656
