00:25:49.016 --> 00:25:50.651
<i>We found something.</i>

314
00:25:51.419 --> 00:25:54.822
(indistinct whispering)

315
00:26:03.364 --> 00:26:04.832
(door closing)

316
00:26:06.500 --> 00:26:07.768
Show me.

317
00:26:25.820 --> 00:26:27.522
Rebecca:
<i>Don't go too far, Gracie.</i>

