she wants us to bring her home.

437
00:37:47.568 --> 00:37:49.070
I need your prayers.

438
00:37:49.704 --> 00:37:53.908
To guide her.
Now, please, pray with me.

439
00:37:58.579 --> 00:37:59.814
Jocelyn: No.

