visions of your daughter?

442
00:38:11.893 --> 00:38:14.262
- Jocelyn, just leave it.
- No, it's okay. It's okay.

443
00:38:14.394 --> 00:38:15.797
No, it's fine.

444
00:38:18.331 --> 00:38:20.467
