your child.

445
00:38:20.968 --> 00:38:23.336
Nor the Nashes,
nor any other human soul.

446
00:38:24.205 --> 00:38:27.608
Then tell me,
who has taken my daughter?

447
00:38:28.976 --> 00:38:32.580
Every year, we drive him out,
