I want to apologize for that.

474
00:39:50.191 --> 00:39:51.659
It's nonsense
what happened today.

475
00:39:51.792 --> 00:39:54.528
You got that? Yeah?
It's nonsense, mate.

476
00:39:54.762 --> 00:39:56.864
Oh, God. Eggs are off.

477
00:39:57.298 --> 00:39:58.766
(knocking on door)

478
00:40:01.535 --> 00:40:04.404
- Henry: Hello.
